mediabox (0.96.1) unstable; urgency=low

  Playlist gets saved after reordering

  Fixed bug where after removing items a list gets stuck and cannot be scrolled
  anymore
  
  Made indexing behavior less optimistic to avoid dead entries

 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Tue, 30 Dec 2008 12:00:00 +0100

mediabox (0.96-2) unstable; urgency=low

  Instant theme switching without the need to restart
  
  New plugin architecture for extending MediaBox
  
  Folder-based browsing
  
  UPnP framework and UPnP AV support
 
  Media bookmarking per file
  
  Shuffle & repeat
  
  Playlist editor and playqueue
  
  Search-as-you-type with finger-friendly on-screen keyboard
  
  File indexing with inotify kernel support and tag-based browsing
  
  Car-mode for easy controlling while driving (play/pause, previous, next)
  
  Bugfixes

 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Sun, 28 Dec 2008 12:00:00 +0100

mediabox (0.95) unstable; urgency=low

  Playlist editor with support for drag-sorting

  Huge memory and speed optimizations (folders with several hundred songs load
  without problems)
  
  Music tracks are sorted by track number if available

  Search-as-you-type for title text in albums and playlists (for models with
  a keyboard)
  
  Revised UI based on user suggestions
    
  Bugfixes

 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Thu, 08 May 2008 19:00:00 +0200

mediabox (0.94.2) unstable; urgency=low

  Fixed integer bug in gconf-workaround module (which is used where gconf
  Python bindings are unavailable due to a packaging bug in pymaemo)
  
  Fixed bug in theme selector touch sensitivity
  
 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Thu, 21 Feb 2008 20:40:00 +0100

mediabox (0.94.1) unstable; urgency=low

  Added support for non-UTF-8 text encodings in ID3 tags
  
  FM radio stops playing when playing other media
  
  Slightly smoother video playback with mplayer
  
  Fullscreen video no longer grabs input
  
  MediaBox no longer hangs at startup after clearing the media collection
  
  Bugfixes

 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Sun, 18 Feb 2008 23:10:00 +0100

mediabox (0.94) unstable; urgency=low

  * Improved caching in media scanner to further minimize scanning time
  
  * Theme enhancements
  
  * Media folders can now be filtered by media content types

  * Automatic detection of memory card replacement (scans for new media)

  * Support for the button on the headset (pause/play)
  
  * Loudspeakers can be switched on for FM radio
  
  * Support for reading FLAC tags

  * Alternative media player backend for the osso-media-server adds support for
  more media formats (such as real media and MP4)
  
  * Bugfixes

 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Sun, 10 Feb 2008 19:10:00 +0100

mediabox (0.93) unstable; urgency=low

  * Highly improved media scanner for quick scanning and quick startup.

  * Support for various ID3 tag versions (v1, v2.2, v2.3, v2.4).
  
  * Support for album art embedded in ID3 tags.
  
  * High-performant GDK-based rendering engine for a responsive UI and
  more transition effects.
  
  * Buttons for skipping and zooming in the image viewer.
  
  * Enhancements in the default theme.
  
  * Application icon now has the proper size on OS 2008.
  
  * Bugfixes
  
 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Mon, 23 Jan 2008 19:13:00 +0100

